'''菲基爾·恩江加西'''（Fikile Ntshangase，{{bd|約1955年||2020年||catIdx=Ntshangase}}）是[[南非|南非]]的一位[[環境保護主義|環境保護主義者]]，她是姆弗魯茲環境正義組織（MCEJO）的領導人，該組織主要的活動為阻止Tendele礦業公司擴張[[赫卢赫卢韦–印姆弗鲁兹公园|赫卢赫卢韦–印姆弗鲁兹公园]]附近{{tsl|en|Open-pit mining|露天採礦|露天}}[[銅礦|銅礦]]的礦場<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-28|title=South African activist killed as contentious coal mine seeks to expand|url=https://news.mongabay.com/2020/10/south-african-activist-killed-as-contentious-coal-mine-seeks-to-expand/|access-date=2021-03-29|website=Mongabay Environmental News}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|last=Koko|first=Khaya|date=7 Nov 2020|title=How we braved danger to honour Fikile Ntshangase|work=Mail & Guardian|url=https://mg.co.za/news/2020-11-07-how-we-braved-danger-to-honour-fikile-ntshangase/|access-date=March 8, 2021}}</ref>。

當地以農牧維生者多支持保護環境，但有些人因工作仰賴礦業而支持礦坑擴建，兩方人士對峙使局勢日益緊張，2020年4月，另一名反煤礦的人士Tholakele Mthethwa的住家即遭開槍恐嚇<ref name=":0" />，附近居民也多次受到暴力威脅，屢傳拒絕遷出祖地者遭到槍擊的案件，同年10月22日晚間，恩江加西在[[誇祖魯-納塔爾省|誇祖魯-納塔爾省]]Somkhele的家中被四名槍手射殺，享年65歲<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-23|title=South African environmental activist shot dead in her home|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/oct/23/south-african-environmental-activist-shot-dead-in-her-home|access-date=2021-03-29|website=the Guardian}}</ref>，她的遇害可能與不久前拒絕在與礦業公司的合同上簽字有關<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-safrica-environment-idINKBN27J2FK|title=South African commission condemns killing of activist who opposed coal mine|publisher=Reuters|date=2020-11-03}}</ref>，其律師受訪時表示恩江加西生前曾說「我絕對不會出賣我的族人，若有必要我會為他們而死<ref name="Greenfield">{{Cite news |last=Greenfield |first=Patrick |date=2020-10-23 |title=South African environmental activist shot dead in her home  |work=The Guardian |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/oct/23/south-african-environmental-activist-shot-dead-in-her-home  |access-date=2021-03-08}}</ref>。」

